Approach:-
- Find the maximum candies among all kids, 
- then check each kid: if candies[i] + extraCandies is greater than or equal to the maximum, 
- add True, otherwise add False.

Code:-
class Solution(object):
    def kidsWithCandies(self, candies, extraCandies):
        l=[]
        maxi = max(candies)
        for i in range(len(candies)):
            if(candies[i]+extraCandies >= maxi):
                l.append(True)
            else:
                l.append(False)
        return l

Time Complexity : O(n)
Space Complexity : O(n)
        
